%% Diagram: Watch Mode Loop
%% Type: flowchart
flowchart TB
    start[Start Watch Mode] --> initial_render[Initial Full Render]
    initial_render --> monitor[Monitor File Changes<br/>chokidar]
    monitor --> change_check{File Changed?}
    change_check -->|Yes| debounce[Debounce 200ms]
    debounce --> rerender[Re-render Changed File]
    rerender --> render_check{Render OK?}
    render_check -->|Yes| update_manifest[Update Manifest]
    render_check -->|No| preserve_output[Preserve Existing Output<br/>Log Error]
    update_manifest --> monitor
    preserve_output --> monitor
    change_check -->|Ctrl+C| dispose[Dispose Browser Pool]
